{"image_id": "CHD_2018_page_95", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "CHURCH & DWIGHT CO., INC. AND SUBSIDIARIES", "bbox": [364.7, 140.2, 873.4, 161.0]}, {"text": "NOTES TO CONSOLIDATED FINANCIAL STATEMENTS—(Continued)", "bbox": [279.5, 177.7, 958.4, 198.5]}, {"text": "(In millions, except share and per share data)", "bbox": [417.3, 202.7, 820.6, 223.5]}, {"text": "11. Stock Based Compensation Plans and Other Benefit Plans", "bbox": [143.8, 252.7, 691.2, 273.5]}, {"text": "The Company has options outstanding under four equity compensation plans. Under the Amended and", "bbox": [185.5, 290.4, 1042.1, 311.3]}, {"text": "Restated Omnibus Equity Plan, the Company may grant options and other stock-based awards to employees and", "bbox": [143.8, 315.4, 1081.7, 336.3]}, {"text": "directors. Under the 1983 Stock Option Plan and the Stock Award Plan, the Company granted options to key", "bbox": [143.8, 340.4, 1051.9, 361.3]}, {"text": "management employees. Under the Stock Option Plan for Directors, the Company granted options to", "bbox": [143.8, 365.4, 987.2, 386.3]}, {"text": "non-employee directors. Following adoption of the original Omnibus Equity Plan by stockholders in 2008, no", "bbox": [143.8, 390.4, 1061.0, 411.3]}, {"text": "further grants were permitted under the other equity compensation plans. Options outstanding under the plans are", "bbox": [143.8, 415.4, 1090.2, 436.3]}, {"text": "issued at market value on the date of grant (with the exception of options granted to former Waterpik employees", "bbox": [143.8, 440.5, 1082.0, 461.3]}, {"text": "as part of the Waterpik Acquisition), vest on the third anniversary of the date of grant and must be exercised", "bbox": [143.8, 465.5, 1047.2, 486.3]}, {"text": "within 10 years of the date of grant. If, upon termination of a participant’s employment (other than a termination", "bbox": [143.8, 490.5, 1083.3, 511.3]}, {"text": "for cause), a participant is at least 55 years old, has at least five years of service, and the sum of the participant’s", "bbox": [143.8, 515.5, 1081.6, 536.3]}, {"text": "age and years of service is at least 65, the participant may exercise any stock options granted in 2007 or later", "bbox": [143.8, 540.5, 1051.3, 561.3]}, {"text": "within a period of three years from the date of termination or, if earlier, the date such stock options otherwise", "bbox": [143.8, 565.5, 1056.1, 586.3]}, {"text": "would have expired, subject to specified conditions. Issuances of Common Stock to satisfy employee option", "bbox": [143.8, 590.5, 1047.1, 611.3]}, {"text": "exercises currently are made from treasury stock.", "bbox": [143.8, 615.5, 555.0, 636.4]}, {"text": "Stock option transactions for the three years ended December 31, 2018 were as follows:", "bbox": [185.5, 665.5, 919.3, 686.4]}, {"text": "Options", "bbox": [747.6, 776.9, 804.1, 793.6]}, {"text": "Weighted", "bbox": [824.8, 726.9, 893.4, 743.6]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [829.4, 743.6, 888.7, 760.2]}, {"text": "Exercise", "bbox": [829.0, 760.2, 889.2, 776.9]}, {"text": "Price", "bbox": [840.5, 776.9, 877.6, 793.6]}, {"text": "Weighted", "bbox": [922.9, 710.2, 991.4, 726.9]}, {"text": "Average", "bbox": [927.5, 726.9, 986.7, 743.6]}, {"text": "Remaining", "bbox": [918.3, 743.6, 996.1, 760.2]}, {"text": "Contractual", "bbox": [914.1, 760.2, 1000.3, 776.9]}, {"text": "Term", "bbox": [937.3, 776.9, 977.1, 793.6]}, {"text": "Aggregate", "bbox": [1021.0, 743.6, 1094.2, 760.2]}, {"text": "Intrinsic", "bbox": [1027.1, 760.2, 1088.2, 776.9]}, {"text": "Value", "bbox": [1036.8, 776.9, 1078.5, 793.6]}, {"text": "Outstanding as of December 31, 2015 . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [143.8, 807.2, 726.8, 828.1]}, {"text": "17.2", "bbox": [757.6, 807.2, 794.1, 828.1]}, {"text": "$25.89", "bbox": [830.4, 807.2, 887.8, 828.1]}, {"text": "Granted . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .", "bbox": [143.8, 832.2, 726.8, 853.1]}, {"text